***
*
* gsFrontend INSTALLATION
*
***

1. Upload all files via FTP

2. Rename the file "/app/cfg.php.dist" to "/app/cfg.php"

3. Configure your gsFrontend installation by editing "/app/inc.cfg.php"

4. Make sure your webserver can write to "/app/templates_c" (chmod 777 templates_c)

5. Finished